Original:
絕對完美的雞翅和薯條。我喜歡一家餐廳像這家餐廳一樣完善簡單的菜單。我唯一的抱怨是，無限量供應的菜單不包括玉米片雞翅，下次我肯定會回來嘗試這些。

當他們說辣時，他們的意思是辣。我的嘴巴因我認為是鬼辣椒而灼痛？雖然喜歡它，但就香料而言，大多數地方都不敢去那裡。那些幽靈胡椒奶昔薯條太好吃了，讓我的嘴麻木了！松露薯條是 A+。

餐廳提供了一份免費的柚子西米甜點以供評論（我實際上沒有兌換，因為我吃飽了吃到飽），但老實說他們不需要，因為我會給無論如何，五顆星。
EN:
Absolutely perfect chicken wings and fries.I like a restaurant as a simple menu like this restaurant.My only complaint is that the menu supplied by the unlimited supply does not include corn slices of chicken wings. Next time I will definitely come back to try these.

When they say spicy, they mean spicy.My mouth is burning because I think it is a ghost pepper?Although I like it, in terms of spices, most places dare not go there.Those ghost peppercorn fans are so delicious, making my mouth numb!Tulu potato strips are A+.

The restaurant provides a free grapefruit sago dessert for comments (I don't actually exchange it because I am full), but honestly, they don't need it because I will give five stars anyway.
